schools.name: Wilson & Young Medal of Honor Middle

data.description: Beautifully maintained FOUR-bedroom home on a corner lot/cul-de-sac street. When you walk in the front door you can't help but notice this SPACIOUS, clean open floorplan. Wood burning fireplace, nicely lit kitchen, beautiful granite countertops, lots of cabinet space, stainless steel appliances, nice size dining area, separate granite breakfast bar sits plenty. HUGE, sequestered master bedroom with roomy garden tub, shower area separate, his/her vanities. Refrigerator stays with the house.
